frameDefinitions: A Donor transfers a Theme from a Donor to a Recipient.
An Agent acts so as to cause some process to begin again after an interruption or suspension.
A Person has a particular mental state and the ability to engage in an activity with enthusiasm, energy, and positivity.
This frame contains words which name permanent fixed structures forming an enclosure and providing protection from the elements.
A Fire burns Fuel, resulting in damage and possibly complete destruction of the Fuel.
Lexical units in this frame refer to Electricity, in particular as a form of energy harnessed for particular uses (such as powering machines).
frameExamples: The two countries <t>revived</t> diplomatic relations after a lull of five years.
The baroque <t>church</t>, built in 1635, has a very rich interior
A fire that started on Saturday afternoon, the High Glade Fire - located on the Mendocino National Forest's Upper Lake Ranger District - continued to <t>burn</t> actively on Sunday.
A compound to generate wind <t>electricity</t> was built on the other side of those mountains.
listRoleDefinitions: The person that begins in possession of the <fen>Theme</fen> and causes it to be in the possession of the <fen>Recipient</fen> .
The entity that ends up in possession of the <fen>Theme</fen>.
The <fen>Time</fen> is when the <fen>Donor</fen> gives the <fen>Theme</fen> to the <fen>Recipient</fen>.
The <fen>Place</fen> where the <fen>Donor</fen> gives the <fen>Theme</fen> to the <fen>Recipient</fen>.
A sentient being acts with the intention of causing a process to begin again.
The process which begins again after a suspension.
The period of time during which the process is suspended.
An animate or inanimate entity, a force, or event that causes the process to resume. Volitionality is not a necessary characteristic of Causes.
The time at which the process is restarted.
The location where the <fen>Agent</fen> causes the <fen>Process</fen> to resume.
The person who is evaluated for a level of enthusiasm.
The entity built by the <fen>Builder</fen> which has some <fen>Function</fen>.

The total material currently involved in combustion, including both the parts of the <fen>Fuel</fen> currently undergoing chemical alteration and the partially ionized gas that results from this process.
The entity that is undergoing rapid chemical alteration leading to damage or destruction.
This role identifies the <fen>Time</fen> when the <fen>Fire</fen> is burning.
This role identifies the <fen>Place</fen> where the <fen>Fire</fen> is burning.
<fen>Electricity</fen> is the physical force that is used as power.
listRoleExamples: <fex>The driver</fex> restarted the truck after it stalled.
The two countries revived diplomatic relations <fex>after a lull of five years</fex>.
<fex>The spring rains</fex> restarted the flow of the stream.
This state reinstated the death penalty <fex>in 1975</fex>.
The two nations revived relations <fex>in Geneva</fex> during the latest round of talks.
The Brunswick Electric Membership Corporation supplies <fex><t>electricity</t></fex> for sections of Brunswick and Columbus counties.

sourceCandidateSpans.text: Sleep No More and Then She Fell
